divs: Sighting Detailsdriving up 5th street in Oregon City I saw five round, glowing orange lights. my friend was driving in front of me and she pulled over. I assumed she saw them too so I pulled over behind her. We both got out of our cars but when we looked up they were gone. I mentioned it to a friend who thought we were crazy but later called me back to inform me that she had received a call from her sister in-law who reported seeing the same things. What I know for sure is at least three people saw them that night.
